title: MADE Show 2024 Video: Builder Roundup #3
content:
Ready for the third batch of bikes from the MADE Show? Of course you are. This time Tyler gets the details on Battaglin, Buendia, Good Grief, Liminal, Seeker, Wheatfall, and Wolfhound. Make sure to check out Roundup #1 and #2 as well!
